e":-21,"quote":{"pid":"198799cc459a503165cde82fb4277fc6b740125d","tid":2263893,"uid":49258,"like":87,"dislike":1,"score":86,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:01:51.000Z","msg":"女職員：屌個毒撚做乜9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:21:13.000Z","msg":"唔毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實係我條女問我，我先走去問個staff<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f109289a1e2f08a8798ed7ba2b76f19badf1524e","tid":2263893,"uid":112185,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"96dd93d2d8874fa748d348570ba7e63f444f1c70","tid":2263893,"uid":114064,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:10:00.000Z","msg":"袋$60一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你問我點答你呀死毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次最多俾你摸吓手仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:22:04.000Z","msg":"$60一個鐘有得摸手仔咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fca49d494ecffbc20488dd1e4778fa22e5ae673","tid":2263893,"uid":112185,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ba48bfe1b66cf675a4c9dd0643fb44b97c0dead0","tid":2263893,"uid":89923,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:11:19.000Z","msg":"咁海洋公園同露營又有咩關係?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:23:03.000Z","msg":"都係呃錢 好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef6a5972de62f445d6189843bc735b9fbbc17b3","tid":2263893,"uid":300782,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:24:17.000Z","msg":"你問埋鯨魚係咪魚"},{"pid":"2bb9d0baf2da23d6db4486b507d81299d728980a","tid":2263893,"uid":117577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:25:59.000Z","msg":"台灣一向叫熊貓做貓熊"},{"pid":"a10ce38f4bdf7103242ea410286f68c4c99a0f25","tid":2263893,"uid":131875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:28:40.000Z","msg":"wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232c8c07bf4e7a2dca5658ce836355e78a537337","tid":2263893,"uid":112185,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"aa068602f10f467fd0ad10c9fece6c2ca31548f3","tid":2263893,"uid":325716,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"5f729b169c2c4b438bc292728d3c0a39bc447034","tid":2263893,"uid":112185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:24:32.000Z","msg":"話說我琴日去海洋公園，睇熊貓既時候突然間想知道熊貓係熊定係貓，之後我去問附近既一個女仔staff，個女仔聽到呢條問題比我嚇親<br />\n<br />\n佢：熊貓應該係熊，同貓應該無乜關係<br />\n我：咁點解熊貓要叫熊貓？<br />\n佢：。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我岩岩又諗起，走左去查Wikipedia，一查就有。原來係因為小熊貓個樣又似浣熊又似貓，之後大熊貓啲骨同牙又好似小熊貓而唔似普通熊，所以又叫埋做熊貓。<br />\n<br />\n但係其實熊貓同小熊貓係兩種好唔同既動物，而且係生物分類學上同貓無乜關係。只係以前啲人唔識，所以亂咁叫，就約定俗成左個名。<br />\n<br />\n希望海洋公園既職員睇到呢個post, 下次識答呢個問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:06:51.000Z","msg":"佢心諗:點解毒撚要叫毒撚?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:31:07.000Z","msg":"我本身想覆你我知，之後我順便Google 左一下，發現我唔知幾時啲野變曬撚<br />\n<br />\n即係本身係叫毒男，而且由來好清楚<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%AF%92%E7%94%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25AF%2592%25E7%2594%25B7&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KK0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=446eb69a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%AF%92%E7%94%B7</a><br />\n<br />\n依家叫毒撚係因為有一排啲野咩都會變左撚，好似耶撚，父幹撚，器材撚，乜撚乜撚。但係最後得毒撚同耶撚仲係咁叫。<br />\n<br />\n但係我唔知幾時開始同幾時消失呢個乜撚文化。點解左膠係左膠唔係左撚呢？"},{"pid":"a7c858287a739798aa0bb036a4a275f3da66ba9b","tid":2263893,"uid":364850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"96dd93d2d8874fa748d348570ba7e63f444f1c70","tid":2263893,"uid":114064,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:10:00.000Z","msg":"袋$60一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你問我點答你呀死毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次最多俾你摸吓手仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:31:17.000Z","msg":"有得摸手仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679b3811fae680a6f56057c8a9397f656f9db592","tid":2263893,"uid":112185,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"6ef6a5972de62f445d6189843bc735b9fbbc17b3","tid":2263893,"uid":300782,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:24:17.000Z","msg":"你問埋鯨魚係咪魚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:32:44.000Z","msg":"一來海洋公園無鯨魚<br />\n二來小學都讀過鯨魚唔係魚<br />\n<br />\n鯨大係咪大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58eb4f19f00380e7a90dd4a3cb809d4ee500a6ed","tid":2263893,"uid":112185,"like":7,"dislike":22,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:37:41.000Z","msg":"咁informative 既post 竟然比人負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人既求知欲同openness 真係好低，outside of conventional schooling system既知識就覺得唔應該同唔需要知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解你覺得你要知道藍鯨係最大既海洋生物，而唔應該知道點解熊貓叫熊貓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0d9445bf6859dd6062b2ca60e7550d56ed1d2b","tid":2263893,"uid":162095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:39:43.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44aa26fe06673fcc514f56334b73efe3545d0e74","tid":2263893,"uid":112185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4f0d9445bf6859dd6062b2ca60e7550d56ed1d2b","tid":2263893,"uid":162095,"like":2,"dislik